BBQ CHICKEN QUESADILLAS IN 90  SECONDS

This is @jeffxtingz go-to lunch and I had to try it. I can’t recommend this more as a healthy, easy lunch idea. 

Recipe Notes:

1. Pair it with veggies to make it a complete meal with the @2bmindset . We got these yummy green beans from @ilanameals and they’re so good. 

2. BBQ sauce: I recommend one without any high fructose corn syrup. This one is called char-b-que bbq sauce. 

3. For wrap: always look for the highest fiber wrap with a minimum of 2g of fiber. This one is whole wheat 

Have you ever made a bbq chicken quesadilla? For a nice shortcut, you can use rotisserie chicken and save an extra few minutes. Whatever you do, try this asap and tag us when you do. We’d love to see it and enjoy along with you. 

#bbqchickenquesadilla #bbqchicken #healthylunch #healthylunchideas #healthyfood #healthymeals #fitfoodie #fitnessjourney #fitfood #easymeals #easymealideas
